Juventus super star Cristiano Ronaldo is the first player in history to win the EPL, La Liga and Seria A. He attained the feat on Saturday after Juventus clinched an eighth-consecutive Serie A crown with a 2-1 victory over Fiorentina. He won the EPL with Manchester United before achieving the same feat with Spanish giants, Real Madrid. The five-time Champion league winner has thus entered history book as the first player ever to win the EPL, La Liga and Serie A.  NAN 